' @desc(USE-SCOPED-REMAP, "`mdd map-scope --cycle N [--base REF] [--json]` (Commands::MapScope) computes which current-side diagrams a cycle's edits could have changed. Project::map_scope diffs source since base (default HEAD) via traceability::changed_code, inverts trace.yml source_links by path to the current @ids that depend on each changed file -> their diagram files, and unions the current-side concepts realizing the manifest's objective scope ids. A changed source file with no source_link is a scope_escape -> full_remap. Exits 0 (a plan).")
title MDD scoped re-map — use case (current)

left to right direction

actor "Developer / Agent" as Dev <<added>>

rectangle "mdd toolchain" {
  usecase "Compute the minimal current-side\nre-map set for a cycle\n(mdd map-scope)" as ScopedRemap
}

Dev --> ScopedRemap

note bottom of ScopedRemap
  Current (USE-SCOPED-REMAP): implemented as
  Project::map_scope + the `mdd map-scope` verb.
  Realized by SEQ-MAP-SCOPE; owned by
  CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE + CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI.
end note
